        "text": "Hebrews 7:14",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "), and the Law had distinctly ordained that “no stranger, which is not of the seed of Aaron, come near to offer incense before the Lord” (",
        "children": []
